{
  "stem": "11000.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He was in the cattle business.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he started his cattle business again there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And life was great.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And my mother's parents also came over and lived with-- in our area.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So life was really beautiful again, until the invasion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Then again, it started to change.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You could see a change.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "The German propaganda started their work, which was very professional.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And you had a Dutch Nazi party.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And you did have Dutch Nazis, all of a sudden, that you didn't think would become Nazis.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But they did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And looking back, I believe that this was more of an economic anti-Semitism, people that saw that they had an advantage [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] financially by being-- becoming Nazis.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But they were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] of course, the first year wasn't that bad, because they had to do a lot of fighting.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They went to Belgium and France and-- but after they-- this was all, so to speak of, taken care of, then, of course, they concentrated on the every day's life.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they started what we call the Jew laws.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Jew laws, I would say, started with we were not allowed to visit public places, like movies, concerts, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] museums, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "There was a curfew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We were not allowed to be on the street after 8:00 at night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And then, of  course, we had to wear the Jew star to identify ourselves all the time that we were Jews.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And the reaction of the Dutch population was, was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I remember when I first wore that Jewish star, people that I never knew and never paid attention to all of a sudden gave me this friendly hello.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And they used the word [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
